data.description: MLS# 269722 FRESHLY PAINTED INTERIOR! Welcome to Meadow Park Estates in South Richland, where you'll find this beautiful 2-story home with tons to offer! With 4 bedrooms, 2.5 bathrooms, and a spacious 2431 sq ft floor plan, this home provides ample space for you and your loved ones. Step inside and be greeted by the fresh new interior paint and trim, creating a bright and inviting atmosphere throughout. The new flooring adds a touch of elegance, while the updated blinds provide privacy and style. The kitchen is a true delight, featuring gorgeous wood cabinetry, granite counters, a convenient breakfast bar, pantry to keep your supplies organized, and updated stainless steel appliances. The formal living room and dining room feature lovely coffered ceilings, and is the perfect space for entertaining and hosting gatherings, while the family room with its cozy fireplace offers a comfortable space for relaxation. The primary bedroom suite is an inviting retreat and includes an extra large closet and spacious private bath. If you’re in need of storage, you will find plenty in the attached 3 car garage. Situated on a .27 acre corner lot, this home offers a fenced backyard, providing privacy, a safe space for outdoor activities, and plenty of room to enjoy gardening. Conveniently located just off Leslie Rd, this home provides easy access to schools, shopping, golfing, and entertainment. Don't miss out on the opportunity to call this beautiful 2-story home your own. With its numerous updates, spacious layout, and fantastic location, it offers the perfect combination of comfort and convenience for everyone.
